-- out/todo.txt --
v3 uses structure sharing (~) for several fields in issue3940 and issue3990,
showing them as shared references rather than expanded inline values.
In particular issue3940.reduced1/2/let show y: ~(X), issue3990 shows _imports
elements as shared references.
